    • Uses of TokenPerLineCorpusReader in com.joliciel.talismane.parser

      Subclasses of TokenPerLineCorpusReader in com.joliciel.talismane.parser 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ParserRegexBasedCorpusReader
      A corpus reader that expects one pos-tagged token with dependency info per line, and analyses the line content based on a regex supplied during construction, via a CorpusLineReader.
      The following placeholders are required:
      CorpusLine.CorpusElement.INDEX, CorpusLine.CorpusElement.TOKEN, CorpusLine.CorpusElement.POSTAG, CorpusLine.CorpusElement.LABEL, CorpusLine.CorpusElement.GOVERNOR.

    • Uses of TokenPerLineCorpusReader in com.joliciel.talismane.posTagger

      Subclasses of TokenPerLineCorpusReader in com.joliciel.talismane.posTagger 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  PosTagRegexBasedCorpusReader
      A corpus reader that expects one pos-tagged token per line, and analyses the line content based on a regex supplied during construction, via a CorpusLineReader.
      The following placeholders are required:
      CorpusLine.CorpusElement.TOKEN, CorpusLine.CorpusElement.POSTAG.

    • Uses of TokenPerLineCorpusReader in com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser

      Subclasses of TokenPerLineCorpusReader in com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  TokenRegexBasedCorpusReader
      A corpus reader that expects one token per line, and analyses the line content based on a regex supplied during construction, via a CorpusLineReader.
      The following placeholders are required:
      CorpusLine.CorpusElement.TOKEN
      These are included surrounded by % signs on both sides, and without the prefix "CorpusElement."
